23,-0.01337184,-0.02752425,0.04264025,0.23419119,0.0609803,0.02117201,-0.02035727,-0.01713351,0.03110393,0.11776376,0.0183958,-0.05573186,0.00082394,0.07157478,-0.00426092,0.01681209,0.04915968,-0.01756098,0.02759867,0.04444272,-0.01150328,0.04622911,-0.01415854,-0.09860869,0.02366292,0.12695554,0.05066631,0.00215629,-0.06273151,0.02706079,0.02944616,-0.03761531,0.00605959,-0.00424687,-0.00728986,0.01772972,0.05574519,-0.0221358,-0.0284044,-0.0103666,-0.01155449,-0.00478931,-0.00962121,0.01568053,0.09294531,0.04604803],"last_embed":{"hash":"1k9d2tj","tokens":496}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1k9d2tj","at":1769676334588},"key":"RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/FY25功底考-题目版(1).md##{89}","lines":[429,429],"size":662,"outlinks":[{"title":"50,59)$ 的被调查者中，投赞成票的男性有 3 人，女性有 2 人，现从该组被调查者中随机选取男女各 2 人进行跟踪调查，求被选中的 4 人中至少有 3 人投赞成票的概率（结果用最简分数表示） 18. 图1 所示的是等腰梯形 $A B C D, A B / / D C, A B=2 D C=4, \\angle A B C=\\frac{\\pi}{3}, D E \\perp A B$ 于 $E$ 点, 现将 $\\triangle A D E$ 沿直线 $D E$ 折起到 $\\triangle P D E$ 的位置, 形成一个四棱雉 $P-E B C D$, 如图 2 所示. (1) 若 $P C=2 \\sqrt{2}$, 求证: $P E \\perp$ 平面 $E B C D$; (2) 若直线 $P E$ 与平面 $E B C D$ 所成的角为 $\\frac{\\pi}{3}$, 求二面角 $P-B C-E$ 的大小. ![","target":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/0Zt5HzujoOWzv0DusZ_NzoSIgl13lhyF3BiwymradllakP98P9t0lYhNI888HHslY6cb8Aj7_aCiP2H3yR8VCbAKITmPlmrk9PZKNgkkLTjXefgiAeVajAWn2Ad85trx.jpeg","line":1}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"1k9d2tj","at":1769676334588}},
